com.stevewedig.blog.symbol

Interface SymbolMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasObjectHelper, Iterable<Map.Entry<Symbol<?>,Object>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SymbolMap.Fluid, SymbolMap.Solid

    public interface SymbolMap
extends Iterable<Map.Entry<Symbol<?>,Object>>, HasObjectHelper
    A type safe mapping from symbols to values of matching types.
